com.pcloud.sdk

Interface RemoteEntry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RemoteFile, RemoteFolder

    public interface RemoteEntry
    An abstraction over a file entry on a pCloud account's filesystem.
    See Also:
    RemoteFile, RemoteFolder

                 boolean overwrite)

        Parameters:

        overwrite - If set to true, a file with the same name in the destination folder will be overwritten
        Returns:
